Implement some new features for the final project.

Add Existing MDL Commands
-------------------------

* Light
  - Define the color & location of a point light source
  - loop through all lights when calculating spec. & diff. reflection

* Mesh
  - import polygons by parsing an external .obj file

* Shading
  - Change how frequently we calculate I

* Set
  - Assign a knob a value

* Setknobs
  - Set all knobs to a value

* Save_coordinate_system
  - Save the current top of the stack to a matrix in the symbol table
  - Only useful if you implement the coordinate system argument when 
  drawing shapes

* Save_knobs
  - Save all current knob values to a list
	  A
	  |
* Tween --|
  - Generate an animation by changing knob values between 2 knob lists

Add New MDL Commands
--------------------

* Add new shapes

* Texture mapping
